8-35:5.2 Comparison of Information Markets and Opinion Pools Through the first screening of various opinion pools, we select Lin All u, Log All u, Log All w, and Log 200 u to compare with predictions from information markets .
8-36:Lin All u as shown in Figure 1 can represent what LinOP can achieve .
