8-65:The first lines of table cells are results for absolute error .
8-66:The second and third lines are dedicated to quadratic score and logarithmic score respectively .
8-67:We can see that, in terms of mean values of accuracy measures, the differences of all methods are not statistically significant to any reasonable degree .
